UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc1='I want Captain Keelhaul to bring The Riptide up to shore from the southeast.  We\'ll send his crew in on foot when the signal is given.  

That big lug, Salthoof, can take the men in swinging.  I want the black spot placed on Revilgaz and Seahorn.  Send \'em right to the bottom of the sea for all I care.

You blokes are responsible for salvaging anything that might be of use for our little project with VanCleef in the Deadmines.' WHERE entry=306; /* text: I want Captain Keelhaul to bring The Riptide up to shore from the southeast.  We\'ll send his crew in on foot when the signal is given.  

