UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc1='Hi Felnok!

My studies in the Burning Steppes are proceeding splendidly.  And I owe $N a lot for all $ghis:her; help!  Here\'s what I need to continue:

A steelcoil bumber-bitzel
A 17-gauge ice-spanner
12 pounds of duck feathers
A jar of that glue you make

Thanks a lot Felnok, and when we see each other again remind me not to put coal in your boots!

-Tinkee' WHERE entry=1691; /* text: Hi Felnok!

My studies in the Burning Steppes are proceeding splendidly.  And I owe $N a lot for all $ghis:her; help!  Here\'s what I need to continue:

A steelcoil bumber-bitzel
A 17-gauge ice-spanner
12 pounds of duck feathers
A jar of that glue you make

Thanks a lot Felnok, and when we see each other again remind me not to put coal in your boots!

-Tinkee */
