UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc1='Here lies King Terenas Menethil II -- Last True King of Lordaeron.

Great were his deeds -- long was his reign -- unthinkable was his death. 

         "May the Father lie blameless for the deeds of the son. 
          May the bloodied crown stay lost and forgotten."
' WHERE entry=1731; /* text: Here lies King Terenas Menethil II -- Last True King of Lordaeron.

Great were his deeds -- long was his reign -- unthinkable was his death. 

