UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc1='Layo:$B$BWe have received the generous help of this fine adventurer.  I have dispatched the adventurer to you in Silithus as a resource.  Please see that such a valuable resource does not go to waste in your efforts to unlock the secrets present there.  The Circle eagerly awaits news of progress.$B$BMay Cenarius watch over you...$BRabine' WHERE entry=2551; /* text: Layo:$B$BWe have received the generous help of this fine adventurer.  I have dispatched the adventurer to you in Silithus as a resource.  Please see that such a valuable resource does not go to waste in your efforts to unlock the secrets present there.  The Circle eagerly awaits news of progress.$B$BMay Cenarius watch over you...$BRabine */
